cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.AR, cs.SY, cs.IT 

This paper discusses the impact of energy consumption on Multipath TCP enabled mobile devices, which is related to network protocols and communication systems (cs.NI). It also touches upon security concerns related to using multiple network paths (cs.CR) and the need for optimizing system performance (cs.AR). The paper also involves theoretical analysis and modeling (cs.SY) and information theory (cs.IT) to formulate the relation between performance and energy consumption.
